19 WHEREAS, the Mountain Home High School Bombers boys' indoor track team
20 claimed its first Class 5A Indoor Track and Field state championship on
21 February 22, 2025, at the Randal Tyson Track Center on the campus of the
22 University of Arkansas in Fayetteville; and
23
24 WHEREAS, team member Connor King finished first in the eight-hundred-
25 meter and sixteen-hundred-meter runs, and bested his personal record by three
26 (3) seconds; and
27
28 WHEREAS, team member Eli Jones finished first in the shot put
29 competition and bested the school record he had set by six inches (6"); and
30
31 WHEREAS, team member Eston Ford had only been training in shot put for
32 two (2) months before the championship, and Head Coach Noah Chagnon noted
33 that the team won the shot put competition overall by only half (1/2) a point
34 and that Ford scored two (2) of the team's points, helping to secure the
35 victory; and
